Comment: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.39,Sora Eng TL note,,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: "Kuni" can be either "country" or "land".
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:46.18,Sora Eng Titles 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(638,127)}A banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:46.18,Sora Eng Titles 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(635,627)}Warfare inside the fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.35,0:01:41.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone hides their secrets within their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:46.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somone said, to uncover those hidden secrets-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:50.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is just like opening a door that should never be opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:56.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the door that can't be opened has an aura of temptation-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:59.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,which attracts people to try and open it no matter what the situation is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:03.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This probably lead to that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:10.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Felicia Heideman erased the records of this incident-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:13.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and she said she wanted to erase it from the Fortress's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I want to record it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:23.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can be sure that there isn't somebody else who will make the same mistake as ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:31.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make note of this shameful incident so as to teach those sheep a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:40.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It started yesterday, when Sister Yumina from the church of Seize paid us a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to make some salads though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The lunch is so splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:54.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We also got those from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:58.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather is hot. So we want to finish them before they go bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a lot of food. Yumina, how about having a meal with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? May I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You got surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:09.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called "Brandy".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...{\alpha&H0FF&}wine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...wine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Calvados, a brandy made from apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:22.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Don't... drinking wine is a sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are still underage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:34.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The church has a rule that people under 20 cannot drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:42.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... if she discovers that this is homemade brandy, it will be big trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:47.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, so please keep it a secret from Yumina and Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,y... ya... Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch is ready, Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:57.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go... got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:11.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to cleanup, so please have your lunch first, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your answer!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? She saw it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:30.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... I will deal with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh...whassup, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:48.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said over there that there's a door that can't be opened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:52.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ye... Yes! That door can't be opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:54.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...right? Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:55.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ye... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was opened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It... it's amazing... right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, Rio-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yumina-chan, how about having a taste of this tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:23.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It... it is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:27.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed right? I learned a new method to make tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about everybody try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It indeed tastes good and the scent is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... this somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:41.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot, how about having some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:46.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, about the other side of the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, something is strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is... is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:06:01.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Kanata-san... Does it look like Rio-san is hiding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:02.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:07.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping secrets is no good! Especially hiding them from your comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I know nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone said there are an infinite number of spirits living in this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:18.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you swear to all these spirits that all you said is true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:24.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:29.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are secrets and worries, I want to share them with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me be your comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:42.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I have a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:45.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a war simulation in this afternoon's training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:49.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kana-chan wins, I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:50.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:53.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine for Kanata as she would find out eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:58.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but if Yumina knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the church knows it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:03.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, please leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:07.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way everyone, how about one more cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:18.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I still owe Kanata a favour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:23.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I pledge on 8 million spirits that-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:31.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not following you because I want to have a try at wearing the uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:34.68,Sora Eng TL note,,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: The kanji for "infinite number of / countless" and "8 million" are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:34.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So... it's not "infinite" now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:37.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks nice on you, Yumina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:41.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan, would you mind helping Kana-chan's team?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:46.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you assign me, I will put my full strength in to the mission. Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So now, I'll explain the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:54.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use water guns during the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:57.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they were used in the Water Festival, there are dyes inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:59.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get dyed if you are hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that is the case, please leave the field. It that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:02.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:04.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ye... Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:10.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have opened the door. If you want to know what is inside, please beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:14.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, start the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Don't get left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:18.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, it's your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gotcha"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:32.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll infiltrate from the dorm's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:32.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:42.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would happen someday, so I prepared this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:46.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:56.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Report: Enemy is located in the depository and is arming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:57.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:04.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving to a place where there's no way to retreat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:07.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they trying to make a last-ditch attempt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do now, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:11.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Check your weapons and ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:13.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We will start attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, you will be responsible for transporting ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a tough task, I'm depending on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:50.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be sacrilegious enjoying war games so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:52.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was really exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:54.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I always used to play this when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:05.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was still young, I used to travel with my merchant father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:09.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother passed away before I was aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I traveled all around the country with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:21.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been to Vingt and even the countryside of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:44.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, since I was traveling around non-stop, I didn't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:51.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I am really happy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:55.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The spirits will definitely forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:11:00.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The infinite spirits here are different from those in Rome, they are generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:08.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:09.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Please wait a minute... We are friends....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:16.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I missed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:23.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But they are scattered. This is a good chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Let's rush in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They are coming, Noël-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:30.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them down in one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:07.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I am not going to show you any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good taste of the power of science!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:11.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:17.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fallback for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold our formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:22.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:29.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooooh!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, we have to find a way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have never imagined that Noël would make something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll attract their attention. You guys find a chance to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:13:00.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I sacrifice my friend to continue living?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:06.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell... My dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Felicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop there. I won't let you pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let you kill Rio and Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:39.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,FELICIA!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:48.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio... Don't die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare... How dare you do this to Felicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,HOW DARE YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How impudent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:13.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:15.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:17.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:18.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've run out of ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:31.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... There are still lots of thing I want to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu... YUMINA-SAN!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:48.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's regrettable... We've tried so hard to make them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:50.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I am calling the medic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:54.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's useless... I know it well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:55.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:59.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata-san... You have to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:03.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... win...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,*dead*
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:48.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will inherit... all of your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:53.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:56.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:13.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:17.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it'd come down to this one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:20.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for me, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, please tell me what this place is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:24.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the distillation plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:31.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are secretly producing wine here to get the capital we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:37.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sacrificed Noël-chan and Yumina-san to conceal the secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:44.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been enjoying this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:45.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you've forgotten about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wages in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:49.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The nice meals you've enjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All these come from this distillation plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:56.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that, can you still point your gun at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:16:58.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't ask me to join...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry about that, Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:14.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would make a good partner to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Same for me, Rio senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have grown much stronger, Kana...ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:40.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I am so glad... You were the one... who defeated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:48.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:59.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Calvados was added to the tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It was nice, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:07.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So... that's why we were so enthusiastic about that silly game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I became more and more serious as I played.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alcohol is really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, things are going along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:22.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I didn't expect that Yumina-chan would be so weak against alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:32.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But please remember, Kana-chan, this is a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Things will get out of control if it is revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:36.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:43.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because, I know you kept it secret from me so as not to get me involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And therefore, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in this sense, I've become a true member of the Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:54.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't call me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:56.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:19:00.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to bath without calling me? I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:04.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I am pure and stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:07.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She started drinking on her own?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:12.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's right... But this is a good chance, wanna try some, Kana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:13.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:17.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also ritual to become a full member of the Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:24.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Well, Platoon leader, I have a bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:28.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:29.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:33.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it now, I should have figured it out from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:38.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The normally supercilious Second Lieutenant Felicia Heideman...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:42.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was too serious in that war game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:57.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Strange as it may seem, Felicia Heideman, the Second Lieutenant, is extremely weak against alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:01.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At that point, she was already drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:09.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really delightful. Am I right, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:14.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And their behavior, later on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:16.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Made me speechless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:19.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to force myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:24.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am a senpai! I am a superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been trying my very best...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:28.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-sama!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:33.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya ya. Senpai is really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:41.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. There are 8 million gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:42.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:46.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, they are totally useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:56.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I will not get drunk no matter how much I drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:21:00.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Fine! Let me sing you a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:09.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So~ ra~ no~ woto hi~ bi~ ke~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:11.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cool, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:14.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that frenzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:20.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I was being interrogated, being the only one awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:27.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a bath together, once more~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but I have to refuse your invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:31.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Let's have some close contact~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:33.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey everyone~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:34.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:36.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:38.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:45.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, till the end, the maidens who turned into ruffian put me into...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I can't write it out anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:22:00.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only good outcome of this incident is that Yumina forgot everything-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:03.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the secret of the fortress can be kept undisclosed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:08.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People who can never get drunk are unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:12.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They have the strongest feelings on the misfortunes that occur when everyone around them get drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:13.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:26.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So... I want to share a wise saying from the ancients with the reader:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:29.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you drink don't get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:31.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're drunk, don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:33.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can drink, but don't if you're drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:35.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Suminoya Kureha
